%% Diagram: AI Agent Workflow
%% Type: sequenceDiagram
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false, 'flowchart': {'htmlLabels': false}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant Agent as AI Agent
    participant CLI as diagramkit CLI (local)
    participant Skills as npx skills (Vercel Labs)
    participant FS as File System

    Agent->>CLI: npm add diagramkit
    Agent->>FS: read node_modules/diagramkit/REFERENCE.md
    Agent->>CLI: npx diagramkit warmup
    CLI->>FS: Install Chromium binary
    Agent->>Skills: npx skills add sujeet-pro/diagramkit
    Skills->>FS: Write diagramkit-* skills under .claude/, .cursor/, .codex/, ...
    Agent->>CLI: npx diagramkit render . --json
    CLI->>FS: Discover diagram files
    CLI->>FS: Write SVG / PNG / JPEG / WebP / AVIF outputs to .diagramkit/
    CLI-->>Agent: JSON result (rendered, skipped, failed)
